Adventures.WEEK1-1, WEEK1-2, WEEK1-3 Beneath Haunte:
{{Main|Beneath Haunted Halls}}
{{Quote|''An attack on a diplomatic mission results in the kidnapping of an eladrin Princess Eldara, and it happens on the PCs' watch! Now they need to find both her and a stolen magic relic before war breaks out in Cormyr. The trail of the villain has more twists than a snake's shadow, and its leads farther than anyone would expect. A Living Forgotten Realms three-round special adventure set in Cormyr for characters levels 1&ndash;4.''}}
* '''Designer(s):''' [[Matthew Sernett]]
* '''Released:''' October 2008
* '''Levels:''' 1{{st}} &ndash; 4{{th}}

Adventures.WEEK1-4 The Icy Queen's Crossing:
{{Main|The Icy Queen's Crossing}}
{{Quote|''In a region so dangerous that even the most savage of Nar tribes fear trespassing there, a group of heroes has a chance to change the face of a war-torn land. This adventure has locations and characters from the Forgotten Realms novel ''The Fall of Highwatch''. A Weekend in the Realms exclusive adventure set in Narfell for Living Forgotten Realms characters levels 1&ndash;4.''}}
* '''Designer(s):''' [[Shawn Merwin]]
* '''Released:''' November 2009
* '''Levels:''' 1{{st}} &ndash; 4{{th}}

